description:
Danny recaps this week's The Real Housewives of Salt Lake City, which featured Seth letting loose and a tubing event, plus The Real Housewives of Potomac, where Karen jumped out of a cake and sent (dead?) butterflies to invite her co-workers to a vow renewal. Danny also dives into Luann's video with Andrew Lloyd Webber and the book drama caused by Not All Diamonds and Rosé.


RHOSLC Recap: 3:00ish

Book Drama: 29:00ish

RHOP Recap: 38:00ish
